question: Are you interested in the UTM ROBOCON Team?
answer: Join our Basic Workshop and Autocar Challenge to gain knowledge and hands-on skills in electronics, programming, and mechanical design! Build your own autocar and compete with other participants to win the race! Benefits include a platform to share innovation, knowledge, and experience with fellow participants, step further into MCU programming and circuit design, boost your resume with technical skills and project experience, hands-on experience with real-world robotics projects, and network and collaborate with robotics enthusiasts. Take your first step towards becoming a ROBOCON member by joining the UTM ROBOCON Recruitment Challenge 2024/25! Don’t miss out! Early bird discounts are available for participants. Link to Registration Google Form: https://forms.gle/VawpDwwxeTPqTGnVA. For more details, visit our website: https://utmrobocon.com/, Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/utm.rbc, or Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/utmrbc.
